  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contact: <a href=\"mailto:remillepattesstudio@gmail.com\">remillepattesstudio@gmail.com</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dimenders</strong> is an online horror game playable in cooperative mode up to 4 players. You and your team have been recruited to investigate the sudden emergence of portals connecting to other dimensions. Your mission is to solve puzzles and find a way to close these portals before they unleash chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The appearance of these portals has allowed dark entities to invade our world. Be warned: they will do anything to stop you progressing. Navigate through perilous levels, confront terrifying dangers and solve complex puzzles, all the while risking your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you succeed in closing the portals, avoiding the entities and solving the mysteries?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/324fce181d596639937b5a1a8c2eaa98.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/324fce181d596639937b5a1a8c2eaa98.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/324fce181d596639937b5a1a8c2eaa98.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here are some features that you will find in the game :</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Inventory System</strong>: Gather and store essential items to aid your progress during missions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Stamina: </strong>Keep an eye on your stamina to avoid exhaustion when it matters most. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Respawning</strong>: Use shared crystals to bring teammates back to life. Pool your resources and work together to ensure everyone survives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Travel </strong>: Move through dimensions while retaining your items for continued exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Proximity chat</strong> : Communicate seamlessly with your team for a more immersive experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And much more..</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/8cf2da9149bac2983410e4e2daa21eeb.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/8cf2da9149bac2983410e4e2daa21eeb.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/8cf2da9149bac2983410e4e2daa21eeb.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/4f78c314818d856ab30406568e6f865e.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/4f78c314818d856ab30406568e6f865e.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/4f78c314818d856ab30406568e6f865e.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Entities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every dimension is teeming with dangerous, cunning entities determined to stop you. Each has its own unique behavior and strategy to neutralize your team. Stay sharp, and don’t let them catch you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/9bfc4b973b175822c867093017e211b4.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/9bfc4b973b175822c867093017e211b4.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/9bfc4b973b175822c867093017e211b4.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expansive Levels</strong>: Explore 4 massive levels, each offering distinct environments and atmospheres.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrifying Creatures</strong>: Encounter over a dozen diverse entities, each with unique behaviors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings</strong>: Discover various outcomes based on your decisions and teamwork.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plenty of Puzzles</strong>: Challenge your logic and teamwork with a variety of original puzzles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/396c0863defba7cdd27af513c6f52842.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/396c0863defba7cdd27af513c6f52842.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/396c0863defba7cdd27af513c6f52842.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contact: <a href=\"mailto:remillepattesstudio@gmail.com\">remillepattesstudio@gmail.com</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dimenders</strong> is an online horror game playable in cooperative mode up to 4 players. You and your team have been recruited to investigate the sudden emergence of portals connecting to other dimensions. Your mission is to solve puzzles and find a way to close these portals before they unleash chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The appearance of these portals has allowed dark entities to invade our world. Be warned: they will do anything to stop you progressing. Navigate through perilous levels, confront terrifying dangers and solve complex puzzles, all the while risking your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you succeed in closing the portals, avoiding the entities and solving the mysteries?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/324fce181d596639937b5a1a8c2eaa98.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/324fce181d596639937b5a1a8c2eaa98.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/324fce181d596639937b5a1a8c2eaa98.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here are some features that you will find in the game :</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Inventory System</strong>: Gather and store essential items to aid your progress during missions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Stamina: </strong>Keep an eye on your stamina to avoid exhaustion when it matters most. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Respawning</strong>: Use shared crystals to bring teammates back to life. Pool your resources and work together to ensure everyone survives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Travel </strong>: Move through dimensions while retaining your items for continued exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Proximity chat</strong> : Communicate seamlessly with your team for a more immersive experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And much more..</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/8cf2da9149bac2983410e4e2daa21eeb.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/8cf2da9149bac2983410e4e2daa21eeb.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/8cf2da9149bac2983410e4e2daa21eeb.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/4f78c314818d856ab30406568e6f865e.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/4f78c314818d856ab30406568e6f865e.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/4f78c314818d856ab30406568e6f865e.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Entities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every dimension is teeming with dangerous, cunning entities determined to stop you. Each has its own unique behavior and strategy to neutralize your team. Stay sharp, and don’t let them catch you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/9bfc4b973b175822c867093017e211b4.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/9bfc4b973b175822c867093017e211b4.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/9bfc4b973b175822c867093017e211b4.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expansive Levels</strong>: Explore 4 massive levels, each offering distinct environments and atmospheres.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrifying Creatures</strong>: Encounter over a dozen diverse entities, each with unique behaviors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings</strong>: Discover various outcomes based on your decisions and teamwork.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plenty of Puzzles</strong>: Challenge your logic and teamwork with a variety of original puzzles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/396c0863defba7cdd27af513c6f52842.poster.avif?t=1739832563\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/396c0863defba7cdd27af513c6f52842.webm?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491620/extras/396c0863defba7cdd27af513c6f52842.mp4?t=1739832563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
